# AI Legacy Navigator — environment variables
#
# OPTIONAL. The app works fully in Demo Mode with no API key at all —
# it generates a complete Legacy Profile, pathways, and 30-day plan
# from structured templates, entirely in the browser.
#
# To enable live AI generation via OpenAI instead, set this on your
# hosting platform (e.g. Vercel project settings) or in a local .env file.
# It is only ever read server-side by api/generate.js — never expose it
# in frontend code, and never commit a real key to git.
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
